<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>AdonisJS - A fully featured web framework for Node.js</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Poppins:400,500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/bulma/0.6.2/css/bulma.min.css">
  <style>
    html, body {
      background-color: #F7F8FA;
      font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
      height: 100vh;
      color: #46444c;
      position: relative;
    }

    body:before {
      content: '';
      background: #5A45FF;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      right: 0;
      height: 6px;
      position: absolute;
    }

    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    a {
      color: #5A45FF;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    main {
      max-width: 620px;
      margin: auto;
      height: 100vh;
      padding: 0 30px;
      align-items: center;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .title {
      font-size: 50px;
      line-height: 50px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      color: #17161A;
    }
    main ul {
      list-style: none;
    }

    main li {
      margin-bottom: 5px;
      position: relative;
      padding-left: 25px;
    }

    main li:before {
      content: 'â€”';
      position: absolute;
      left: 0;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <main>
    <div>
      <h1 class="title"> welcome! </h1>

      <ul>
        <li>
          If you run into problems, you can reach us on <a href="https://discord.gg/vDcEjq6?">Discord</a>.
        </li>
      </ul>
      <br>
      <div class=" flex gap-2">
        <a href="/login" class="button">Se connecter</a>
        <a href="/register" class="button">S'incrire</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
